      2           *  @file       APIMotorControl.c
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      This module provides a link between the Reveal and the Mci API.
      5           *
      6           *  @details    Parse all commands from Reveal, link with Mci API, build up the data accordingly and
      7           *              provides the related feedback to the Reveal protocol.
